snippet.title: Official Release Trailer Galaxy Life (2022)
snippet.description:
It's finally time, after 6 years Galaxy Life is back!

Galaxy Life is finally back and ready to be played again, are you ready to colonize planets and participate in epic alliance wars? Play Galaxy Life now on steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1927780/Galaxy_Life/
